137
00:08:52.790 --> 00:08:55.227
knowing how to take care of yourself is another.
而知道如何照顾自己则是另一回事。

138
00:08:56.523 --> 00:08:59.100
Along those same lines, when we talk to parents,
同样地，当我们和父母们聊天时，

139
00:08:59.124 --> 00:09:04.619
